00:28:26,890 --> 00:28:28,300
No.

287
00:28:29,180 --> 00:28:31,820
May I have a word with Mr Wen?

288
00:28:39,210 --> 00:28:40,200
Mr Wen.

289
00:28:40,890 --> 00:28:42,570
My sewing has improved.

290
00:28:42,930 --> 00:28:45,370
Does this look like a little fat fish?

291
00:28:47,870 --> 00:28:49,970
When can you come back?

292
00:28:50,360 --> 00:28:51,510
According to Madam,

293
00:28:51,610 --> 00:28:53,540
His Majesty already pardoned you.

294
00:28:53,820 --> 00:28:56,600
You're to protect
Queen Dowager Wen and Duke An.

295
00:28:56,690 --> 00:28:58,150
His Majesty is kind to you.

296
00:28:58,390 --> 00:28:59,710
This time,

297
00:29:00,860 --> 00:29:03,590
it'll take at least ten years
for you to come back.

298
00:29:03,880 --> 00:29:05,200
This purse is for you.

299
00:29:05,480 --> 00:29:07,680
Keep it with you.

300
00:29:09,330 --> 00:29:10,790
I won't come back anymore.

301
00:29:14,770 --> 00:29:16,480
There is no way Duke An and I

302
00:29:17,810 --> 00:29:19,610
could redeem the wrongs we made.

303
00:29:26,290 --> 00:29:27,660
You made a nice purse.

304
00:29:32,980 --> 00:29:34,310
Give it to someone else.

305
00:29:39,880 --> 00:29:41,080
Your Majesty.

306
00:29:42,980 --> 00:29:43,940
Let's go.

307
00:30:19,600 --> 00:30:22,360
[Marriage Agreement]

308
00:30:20,790 --> 00:30:21,670
Good.

309
00:30:26,800 --> 00:30:27,700
Duke Su.

310
00:30:28,710 --> 00:30:30,380
It was a challenging trip.

311
00:30:31,300 --> 00:30:32,570
You've succeeded.

312
00:30:32,660 --> 00:30:34,190
The credit should go to you.

313
00:30:34,570 --> 00:30:36,010
I am very happy.

314
00:30:36,650 --> 00:30:38,450
You'll be handsomely rewarded.

315
00:30:39,750 --> 00:30:40,840
Thank you, Father.

316
00:30:45,700 --> 00:30:46,600
Father.

317
00:30:47,290 --> 00:30:48,930
I have a request.

318
00:30:49,880 --> 00:30:51,050
What is it?

319
00:30:52,610 --> 00:30:55,530
The organisation you
asked me to investigate,

320
00:30:56,120 --> 00:30:57,650
it's called Ruyi Pavilion.

321
00:30:57,700 --> 00:30:58,900
Ruyi Pavilion.

322
00:30:59,400 --> 00:31:03,120
I hope you could summon
the owner of Ruyi Pavilion,

323
00:31:03,570 --> 00:31:04,450
Fu Rong.

324
00:31:11,630 --> 00:31:16,230
Summon the owner of Ruyi Pavilion,
Fu Rong to the imperial court.

325
00:31:32,030 --> 00:31:33,920
Your Majesty.

326
00:31:35,790 --> 00:31:37,400
Duke Su told me,

327
00:31:37,820 --> 00:31:40,020
you're the owner of Ruyi Pavilion.

328
00:31:40,660 --> 00:31:41,550
Yes.

329
00:31:42,910 --> 00:31:43,800
Fu Rong,

330
00:31:44,710 --> 00:31:46,540
I've underestimated you.

331
00:31:47,270 --> 00:31:48,270
Did you know

332
00:31:48,740 --> 00:31:51,460
I ordered Ruyi Pavilion to be destroyed?

333
00:31:53,890 --> 00:31:55,940
Since you're the owner,

334
00:31:56,220 --> 00:31:58,020
you should be arrested.

335
00:31:58,830 --> 00:31:59,710
Your Majesty.

336
00:32:00,710 --> 00:32:03,840
Ruyi Pavilion uses information
to help uphold justice.

337
00:32:04,020 --> 00:32:07,150
Only the brave and righteous
are found in Ruyi Pavilion.

338
00:32:07,580 --> 00:32:10,710
But they were taken advantage of
to engage in bad things.

339
00:32:11,150 --> 00:32:12,550
In my hand

340
00:32:12,970 --> 00:32:14,970
is a token to command Ruyi Pavilion.

341
00:32:15,060 --> 00:32:16,080
I bring it here

342
00:32:16,410 --> 00:32:17,410
for your usage.

343
00:32:19,530 --> 00:32:20,430
Your Majesty.

344
00:32:21,200 --> 00:32:22,960
[Decree]

345
00:32:26,370 --> 00:32:27,410
Stand up.

346
00:32:28,220 --> 00:32:29,220
Thank you.

347
00:32:33,000 --> 00:32:33,900
Father.

348
00:32:34,890 --> 00:32:37,040
I was able to return alive

349
00:32:37,660 --> 00:32:40,980
all because of Ruyi Pavilion's help.

350
00:32:42,080 --> 00:32:43,880
It is like a double-edged sword.

351
00:32:43,910 --> 00:32:44,870
Good or bad,

352
00:32:45,380 --> 00:32:46,750
it depends on the user.

353
00:32:47,670 --> 00:32:49,930
It takes orders from the royal court now.

354
00:32:50,700 --> 00:32:52,030
It could be very useful.

355
00:32:59,190 --> 00:33:00,190
Deliver my order.

356
00:33:00,660 --> 00:33:03,030
Stop all actions against Ruyi Pavilion.

357
00:33:04,230 --> 00:33:05,960
Those working in Ruyi Pavilion

358
00:33:07,320 --> 00:33:09,000
will be reorganised.

359
00:33:09,780 --> 00:33:11,190
Duke Su will be in charge of

360
00:33:11,190 --> 00:33:13,660
the Department of Internal Affairs.

361
00:33:14,980 --> 00:33:16,500
Thank you, Your Majesty.

362
00:33:17,720 --> 00:33:18,610
Father.

363
00:33:19,660 --> 00:33:21,810
I have another request.

364
00:33:22,080 --> 00:33:23,310
What is it?

365
00:33:25,980 --> 00:33:27,140
Please allow me

366
00:33:28,810 --> 00:33:30,680
to divorce

367
00:33:31,230 --> 00:33:32,160
Concubine Rong.

368
00:33:34,510 --> 00:33:43,570
[A Beautiful Day]

369
00:34:06,640 --> 00:34:08,500
Both of you are being ridiculous.

370
00:34:09,139 --> 00:34:10,900
When I first received the news,

371
00:34:10,980 --> 00:34:12,590
I almost fainted.

372
00:34:15,550 --> 00:34:16,699
Duke Su insisted.

373
00:34:16,790 --> 00:34:17,989
I had no choice.

374
00:34:19,449 --> 00:34:20,610
In Dayu,

375
00:34:20,920 --> 00:34:23,780
