promote concubine to wife.

376
00:34:23,889 --> 00:34:24,790
So,

377
00:34:25,580 --> 00:34:26,980
Duke Su wanted to give me

378
00:34:27,070 --> 00:34:29,670
an official wedding fit
for a legitimate wife.

379
00:34:31,130 --> 00:34:32,080
He said

380
00:34:32,380 --> 00:34:35,440
he wants me to wear the Phoenix Crown
in a decent manner.

381
00:34:42,030 --> 00:34:42,920
Sister.

382
00:34:43,610 --> 00:34:44,860
I've married twice.

383
00:34:44,949 --> 00:34:46,610
When will be your turn?

384
00:34:46,900 --> 00:34:47,900
She's right.

385
00:34:49,670 --> 00:34:50,780
I...

386
00:34:52,580 --> 00:34:53,610
Your Highness.

387
00:34:54,260 --> 00:34:55,230
Your Highness.

388
00:34:55,670 --> 00:34:56,730
The time has come.

389
00:34:56,820 --> 00:34:57,820
Come out now.

390
00:34:59,190 --> 00:35:01,190
He's in time. Go now.

391
00:35:06,110 --> 00:35:07,260
Look at her.

392
00:35:11,590 --> 00:35:12,470
Your...

393
00:35:18,450 --> 00:35:19,340
Xuan'er.

394
00:35:19,730 --> 00:35:20,790
What's the matter?

395
00:35:23,600 --> 00:35:24,600
The time has come.

396
00:35:25,360 --> 00:35:26,250
Step back.

397
00:35:27,940 --> 00:35:28,990
Step back.

398
00:35:36,590 --> 00:35:37,470
Close the door.

399
00:35:39,110 --> 00:35:40,470
What is this supposed to mean?

400
00:35:40,470 --> 00:35:42,390
-Don't close it.
-Little Marquis.

401
00:35:42,390 --> 00:35:43,710
-We hold the door.
-Xuan'er.

402
00:35:43,710 --> 00:35:44,670
To go in,

403
00:35:44,790 --> 00:35:46,720
-you need to pay.
-Red packet money.

404
00:35:46,720 --> 00:35:47,720
Red packet money?

405
00:35:48,390 --> 00:35:49,740
Bai Qi.

406
00:35:49,830 --> 00:35:51,300
I want a hug.

407
00:35:51,390 --> 00:35:52,990
Guan Ge,

408
00:35:53,110 --> 00:35:54,640
are you here to join the fun?

409
00:35:54,800 --> 00:35:55,730
Bai Qi.

410
00:35:55,810 --> 00:35:57,530
Give me red packet.

411
00:35:57,620 --> 00:35:59,470
Little Marquis, why do you stand there?

412
00:35:59,470 --> 00:36:00,870
-Where's the money?
-No.

413
00:36:00,890 --> 00:36:02,450
Nobody asked me to prepare for it.

414
00:36:02,450 --> 00:36:04,310
You'll have to get it from Duke Su.

415
00:36:05,080 --> 00:36:06,530
It's fine, I have an idea.

416
00:36:06,740 --> 00:36:08,920
