a lucrative red packet money.

447
00:37:12,810 --> 00:37:14,380
What's the matter with you?

448
00:37:14,480 --> 00:37:16,410
Stop making fun of me at this point.

449
00:37:19,470 --> 00:37:20,360
Here.

450
00:37:26,630 --> 00:37:28,030
Put on the Phoenix Crown.

451
00:37:28,540 --> 00:37:29,860
Our Rong'er

452
00:37:30,870 --> 00:37:32,470
is getting married.

453
00:39:01,020 --> 00:39:02,810
[Duke Su's Residence]

454
00:39:56,680 --> 00:39:57,560
Duke Su.

455
00:40:08,420 --> 00:40:10,220
