456
00:40:15,120 --> 00:40:16,050
My dear husband.

457
00:40:42,130 --> 00:40:44,990
[Elegant and Peaceful]

458
00:41:17,600 --> 00:41:19,000
Did you have a good dream?

459
00:41:19,840 --> 00:41:20,800
You're happy.

460
00:41:21,400 --> 00:41:23,470
I had a dream like last time.

461
00:41:23,870 --> 00:41:25,650
But the nightmare became a sweet dream.
